FBIS3-21682 "jptdd009__l94080" JPRS-TDD-94-009-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 28 February 1994 AFRICA SOUTH AFRICA Nigerian Arrested With 1.5 Kg of Cocaine MB2202155994 Johannesburg Afrikaans Stereo Radio Network in Afrikaans 1400 GMT 22 Feb 94 MB2202155994 Johannesburg Afrikaans Stereo Radio Network Language: Afrikaans Article Type:BFN [Text] A Nigerian was arrested at Jan Smuts Airport outside Johannesburg today after about 1.5 kilograms of cocaine, with a street value of 405,000 rands, was found in his baggage. The police said the 29-year-old man had been a passenger on a flight from Rio de Janeiro in Brazil to Harare in Zimbabwe. He was to appear in court today.
